p: Statistical analysis was interpreted as mean ± SEM. The values obtained were compared with the control group and considered statistically significant ( ***p < 0.001, **p < 0.01 and *p < 0.05) followed by One-way analysis of variance (ANOVA) with Dunnett's test. All statistical analyses were performed using GraphPad Prism Version 5.2 (San Diego, CA).
